search_results.title: Eli Clare
search_results.snippet: Eli Clare (born 1963) is an American writer, activist, educator, and speaker. His work focuses on queer, transgender, and disability issues.

search_results.title: Eli Friedman - The ILR School - Cornell University
search_results.snippet: Eli Friedman has a PhD in sociology from the University of California, Berkeley and has been on the faculty of the ILR School since 2011.
